<p>https://www.fda.gov/consumers/consumer-updates/otc-cough-and-cold-products-not-infants-and-children-under-2-years-age </p>
<p>[2] The common cold in children:Management and prevention via UpToDate. </p>
<p>[3] 医药导报，2017年第8期 </p>
<p><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201025/2b5e44d6eb0b47c7aa421d03e25adfaf.jpeg" height="688" width="882" /></p>
<p>本文经首都医科大学附属北京儿童医院儿科药师 徐晓琳 审核 </p>
